Class Parameter

java.lang.Object
  Parameter
Direct Known Subclasses:
ColorParameter, DoubleParameter, IntParameter
public abstract class Parameter
extends java.lang.Object

Class Parameter - a superclass which represents the basic properties of a parameter used in a simulation: the parameter's name and whether or not it is adjustable during the running of the simulation it is used in. This class is supposed to be sub-classed for different types of parameter such as Double, Int, Color etc.

Version:
1 (03/11/2010)
Author:
Robin Smith
